  • Stay Connected to Call & View Messages Freely: You can easily answer/make calls and receive message notifications (such as WhatsAPP, SNS, etc.) on the watch . What's even more impressive is its newly upgraded detection technology that enables you to measure them simultaneously with just one click, saving time and ensuring efficiency. The activity watch will monitor your sleep and breathing quality in real time, which keeps you informed of the basic health status. The health watch can remind you to drink water, wash hands and move around. For women, it thoughtfully include a menstrual cycle tracking feature to manage your period.
  • Various Sports Watch & IP68 water resistance: You can add 20 sports types on watch from 100+ sports choices in the APP. It can intelligently recognize the exercise when you are running and walking. You can view time duration, calories, distance, average/max pace, aerobic training effect, and more detail data on watch and view more analysis in APP. The color is exactly as pictured in real life, a cross between Bordeaux, Merlot, and Burgundy its beautiful, and a lovely change from the usual black go-to for a neutral color? I use it for the time feature, and for walking and running. And as we know, all straps arent created equal; some are too long or too short this one is exactly right, and I dont have small wrists. Its so comfortable, since I put it on, I actually checked a few times to see that its still there. Yup! Others Ive worn with generous length straps have been too long, thick, and sweaty, to be honest. This one is thin, and lightweight. What's not to like. : ) Before installing the VeryFit app, the included instructions tell you to charge the watch, but when I attached it to the charger, it was at 95%, so I was good to go right out of the box and could set it up and wear it immediately which I did! For watch faces, the free options available are plentiful. I found two I wanted (see photos), one to keep me motivated to "keep moving. I like to see my accumulated steps. The battery life is claimed to last up to 20hrs, but faces I choose include battery % a must for me, 'cuz I can forget to charge my watch,. I like how the app is designed to recognize exercises like running and walking; you can add 20 sports from 100+ options in the VeryFit app, which is easy to use (even for me whos not super techy), and Im very into how it can set up GPS routes for my exercise. Personally, I don't set it to receive texts or calls because I already have enough devices buzzing, including work and personal. So I prefer it as a simple, stylish watch that helps me stay on track to remember to keep on moving. I also find the flashlight function is a bonus for after-dark moments when you need to see into your purse, or to illuminate a lock when someone forgets to turn on the outdoor lights! I think this watch is a great buy for anyone, whether for workouts or as a nice watch accessory, she's a looker. ; ) Its already my new favorite and I'm picky. ; ) I wore it to workout this morning and was asked where I got it. (the color is so nice, with its rose gold face.) Very pleased with this. : )
